### Register
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "demo",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "demo",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

### Refresh token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "demo",
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### Create group
POST http://localhost:8080/api/groups
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Личное"
}

### Bulk create tasks
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "groupId": "{{groupId}}",
  "titlesRaw": "Молоко.Фрукты.Овощи",
  "description": "Купить сегодня"
}

### Complete task
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isCompleted": true
}

### History
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Sync pull
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sync/pull?since=2026-01-01T00:00:00.000Z
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
